{"tid":489194,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻狗出街前慘叫","createTime":"2017-12-04T12:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T18:30:11.000Z","uid":141802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3fddae8624e6846fb2186a7951749ce6d00dd74d","tid":489194,"uid":141802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"我隻狗以前出街都好正常<br />\n好乖咁戴繩<br />\n又會好開心<br />\n但近依一兩個月開始<br />\n唔知點解每次我老豆話要帶佢出街既時候<br />\n佢就會走去枱底 &ldquo;呢&rdquo;埋<br />\n（如果我同我呀媽係屋企既話）<br />\n佢就會走泥搵我同我呀媽<br />\n一路fing 尾一路慘叫<br />\n一路用手 &ldquo;wer&rdquo;我同呀媽隻手<br />\n但係當我地想掂佢個陣<br />\n佢就好惡咁要咬手<br />\n我老豆幫佢戴繩佢又唔係好想<br />\n好似唔想出街咁<br />\n條繩放係地下<br />\n我要拎個陣佢又會護繩咁好惡<br />\n<br />\n但重點係，如果係我要帶佢出街個陣佢好開心好乖<br />\n好聽話咁戴繩<br />\n又唔會慘叫<br />\n好正常架bo<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知道點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇方法可以解決<br />\n見到佢咁慘叫 好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59a2264e32d7072a17094a9858b9c2ef50f683a","tid":489194,"uid":141167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:23:15.000Z","msg":"係咪你老豆喺出面打佢？"},{"pid":"5f870e1e555e3396234d4087ae3d362b0589e0b7","tid":489194,"uid":141802,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪你老豆喺出面打佢？</blockquote><br />\n 又唔會呀 <br />\n佢地出街好開心<br />\n老豆同佢玩波波<br />\n出完街都好開心<br />\n同埋我隻狗出街都好乖<br />\n<br />\n但佢平時日日都會周圍係屋企柯尿<br />\n我老豆第一個番屋企<br />\n見到佢鬧 同埋罰佢坐係到 （我平時都會咁做）<br />\n不過我老豆會打下佢patpat咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我媽夜晚帶佢出街佢都會慘叫咁<br />\n但我呀媽又唔會鬧佢又唔會打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0b0e25cf88a45d65b986423f6f1858f09b7863","tid":489194,"uid":25463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:51:31.000Z","msg":"幾大？男定女？絕育未"},{"pid":"cd7605f0647a82632dcf3a54d17f048b6091fce6","tid":489194,"uid":126293,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"你老豆近排有冇覺得膀頭好攰，好似有人坐住咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00cb9064d8813c176ae720a81ca5107787abaae","tid":489194,"uid":51399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老豆近排有冇覺得膀頭好攰，好似有人坐住咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbe078b0cdd79913218568f3648962b48473f0c","tid":489194,"uid":138420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你老豆近排有冇覺得膀頭好攰，好似有人坐住咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c288459e04a832a7ce49201823aa031b7ab23f65","tid":489194,"uid":141802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾大？男定女？絕育未</blockquote><br />\n三歲 男仔。絕左啦<br />\n同埋呢我老豆只要唔係夜晚帶佢出去<br />\n佢都唔會咁<br />\n又係好開心好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cffd82f47e1721ebb139d9a20f7eca66213e038","tid":489194,"uid":25463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:12:58.000Z","msg":"似係你老豆嚇親佢<br />\n如果你老豆比野佢食佢食唔食<br />\n建立返個關係先啦"},{"pid":"06ceb4377c7a2dadf2b8b39c3317c4db37e284b5","tid":489194,"uid":104748,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T19:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你老豆近排有冇覺得膀頭好攰，好似有人坐住咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3條on9仔摺柒埋啦傻閪"},{"pid":"03ab2610a892e4c255c5f6bbc2b94a4d06da9550","tid":489194,"uid":52040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T00:59:05.000Z","msg":"之前有馴狗巴打話，狗係會認定一個人為master, 同你一齊冇異常 ，會係依個原因？"},{"pid":"1da34f978eb0416f503c52f1563295ad61d71fb4","tid":489194,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你老豆近排有冇覺得膀頭好攰，好似有人坐住咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係on9仔摺柒埋啦傻閪</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d39748ea1a5e5e1af2eff9301f9d5cd5a18b10c","tid":489194,"uid":141802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似係你老豆嚇親佢<br />\n如果你老豆比野佢食佢食唔食<br />\n建立返個關係先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢一有食物就會好痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似今朝早我老豆帶佢出去都唔會叫<br />\n好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞唔明"},{"pid":"8a1f8acdcfdb4a847574e9b72282ee129fc54b12","tid":489194,"uid":141802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前有馴狗巴打話，狗係會認定一個人為master, 同你一齊冇異常 ，會係依個原因？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有機會<br />\n因為係屋企佢least favourite person 係我老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但養左幾年係依幾個月先咁<br />\n就覺得好怪<br />\n定係佢係叫我陪佢一起出街呢？"},{"pid":"344c42dffeef215a46bde7a2e56084d90c023af5","tid":489194,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"我果隻好睇心情<br />\n有時好想出，有時又唔理你"},{"pid":"fe0d796256bcf6c7b99a8c31d98115152cc06433","tid":489194,"uid":139552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T18:30:11.000Z","msg":"呢啲有得教喎 <br />\n我男朋友係領犬員 有興趣可以放低tg傾下"}]}